[
  "Takanori Nakamura is the founder and CEO of cloud software firm Rakus, which offers cloud-based solutions for small and medium business enterprises.",
  "Rakus was founded in 2000 and went public in 2015.",
  "Rakus's flagship product is its expense management software, Rakuraku Seisan.",
  "Nakamura has a stated ambition of making Rakus one of the top 100 listed enterprises in Japan by 2030 in terms of market capitalization."
